<script>
function kiemTra() {
const value = document.getElementById('checkInput').value.trim();
const result = document.getElementById('checkResult');
if (!value) {
result.innerHTML = '<div class="alert danger">Vui lng nhp thng
tin!</div>';
return;
}
const blackList = ['scam', 'nhanqua', 'lixi', 'free', '012345'];
let isScam = blackList.some(word => value.toLowerCase().includes(word));
if (isScam) {
result.innerHTML = '<div class="alert danger"> Cnh bo: C du hiu
nghi vn!</div>';
} else {
result.innerHTML = '<div class="alert safe"> Cha pht hin trong danh
sch en.</div>';
}
}
</script>
